<h4 id="3-process-technology-trend">3. Process Technology Trend</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Gate density doubles at each node</li>
  <li>with more integrated functions and features</li>
  <li>with higher performance</li>
  <li>with lower active and static power</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="4-gate-density-mmm2-65nm--x2--45nm--x2--32nm">4. Gate Density (M/mm^2): 65nm → x2 → 45nm → x2 → 32nm</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Relative Performance (Ring Oscillator): 65nm → 23% up → 45nm → 45% up → 32nm</li>
  <li>Relative Power: 미세화 공정을 한 단계 거칠수록 평균 Active Power/MHz 25% Down, Standby Leakage 50% Down</li>
</ul>

